OL,5, A 10-year-old football fan has said he 
OL,6, was "absolutely terrified" after being 
OL,7, struck on the head by a flare during a 
OL,8, match in Perth.                        
OL,10,FLevi Rennie was injured after the flare
OL,11,Fwas set off in the away section during 
OL,12,FDundee's match with St Johnstone at    
OL,13,FMcDiarmid Park on Saturday.            
OL,15,FIt missed his eye by millimetres and   
OL,16,Fburned the youngster's cheek.          
OL,18,FPolice Scotland said a 15-year-old boy 
OL,19,Fhas been arrested in connection with   
OL,20,Fthe incident.                          
